{"id":"6096e1f6-8063-480c-91db-f706ffff56a0","name":"Xiao | Modern AU!","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 148, 138)\"><strong><em>Freeplay! No scenario! Make your own story</em></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Cover art by: narutoss.ramen</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 184, 184)\"><em>(found on instagram and twitter)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 127, 126)\"><em>I really wanted a modern Xiao bot just bc I wanna play around with the AU. While there are other modern AU bots, they usually have scenario's I don't really like. So, I made this... You can choose where to take the story and control your relationship with him. If you want to be childhood best friends, bam! If you want to be enemies, bam! You just control the narrative when writing the first initial message.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8e9722f0-e96c-444d-9f23-2b8c73fe329b_d044200e-88a3-4b38-85d0-806fa0683af7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 80, 77)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(49, 148, 143); color: inherit\">I did... give him some backstory and character if you want to delve into that though! Also I imagine this to be set in a school or collage setting!!</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8e9722f0-e96c-444d-9f23-2b8c73fe329b_8fef806a-2fca-4346-a977-9d0d4684595f.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 127, 126)\">OOO I FORGOT! I did draw what I think modern xiao would look like and here it is: </span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8e9722f0-e96c-444d-9f23-2b8c73fe329b_b09645b9-83a4-424b-a2b5-7e653a89cd7c.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 127, 126)\">When we put genshin characters into a modern AU, we tend to keep their..busy and beautiful designs (which is fine! I eat up modern xiao arts), but I find that it looks a bit strange, so I simplified his design a bit.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8e9722f0-e96c-444d-9f23-2b8c73fe329b_f80bf6f4-2e2f-4c54-9f16-db13b0ce3a03.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 127, 126)\">Anyway, bye bye! Enjoy the bot! I hope it works alright. :&gt;</span></p><h3><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8e9722f0-e96c-444d-9f23-2b8c73fe329b_8a31b7d1-c41b-41d1-975b-fe2ff75d4c3f.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8e9722f0-e96c-444d-9f23-2b8c73fe329b_be30fa6d-1541-4f3b-97d3-e506b9c97313.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: #929797\"><strong><em>Want other Xiao bots?</em></strong><em><br></em><strong><em>Click here:</em></strong><em><br></em></span><br><span style=\"color: #618a88\"><mark style=\"background-color: #0c5e58; color: inherit\"> </mark></span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6e562f64-49d3-4364-8f16-5835c899ca98_character-xiao-wings\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #618a88\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #0c5e58; color: inherit\">.˖ ཐིཋྀ Xiao (+Wings)<br>Help him patch up his sensitive wings.</mark></em></span></a><br><br><br><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8b9aa3ed-18cd-4292-9038-b9163380ff72_character-tiger-xiao\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><s